headers.subject: [tosdr:2142] "Business Transfers" ratings?

html:
Why do some services (SoundCloud, Delicious) get a bad rating, while other services (Cloudant, Couchsurfing) get a neutral rating, despite having (as far as I can tell) the same conditions (i.e. data will be transferred without prior notice)?
